**if `log` is `false`**

`x`: approximated solution.

**if `log` is `true`**

`x`: approximated solution.

`ch`: convergence history.

**ConvergenceHistory keys**

`:atol` => `::Real`: atol stopping tolerance.

`:btol` => `::Real`: btol stopping tolerance.

`:ctol` => `::Real`: ctol stopping tolerance.

